	t limit per patron. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will have their ord
	ers cancelled at the venue's discretion. All sales are final. No refunds o
	r exchanges. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have a ticket regar
	dless of age. No babies in arms. Mobile ticket delivery will be delayed un
	til 4 days prior to event.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive e
	arly. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing ADA acc
	essible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance is
	 needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at acc
	essibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless freesta
	nding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and their companions. Pl
	ease note that our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony levels.
	\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/alyssa-edwards-thanks-for-everything-tour
	-seattle-washington-04-09-2026/event/0F0064369B457D91\n\nFrom STG - Neptun
