	 ticket limit may be cancelled without notice. All sales are final. No ref
	unds or exchanges. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Ve
	nue reserves the right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\
	, each person must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. The
	re is no elevator. Stairs and ramps only to the balcony level.\nMetal dete
	ctors & bag search at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/
	about/safety When purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to 
	contact us by email if assistance is needed with accommodations or compani
	on seating\; you may reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each acces
	sible seat houses an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility 
	impairments and their companions. Please note that our historic theatre ha
	s no elevator to the balcony levels. The ADA section on the seating map do
	es not represent a specific seat location.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com
